data.description: Don't wait on this beautiful rural retreat! This 4 bed, 3 bath ranch with 3476 sq. ft. sits on 35 fully fenced acres with a fantastic view of Pikes Peak! Home has been remodeled and updated. Brand new roof and stucco, new tile, newer carpet, newer oversized furnace/AC, newer water heater, newer radon system, new front door & storm door, and fresh paint throughout. Electric gate for security. Primary bedroom and bath have been completely remodeled, and opens to back deck. Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, custom cabinets with soft-close doors & slides, and island with breakfast bar. Spacious open floor plan with gas fireplace, walkout to expansive Trex deck that spans the length of the house, and flex space that can function as a second dining room, office, media room, or could be converted to a bedroom. Convenient main level laundry and bluetooth enabled ceiling fan in main bathroom. Partially finished basement includes 2 large bedrooms, bathroom with standup shower, toilet, and double vanity, huge living space perfect for a theater or pool table, mechanical room with plenty of storage space, another large storage closet, and unfinished area for workout equipment, storage, or to finish as you like. Oversized 2 car garage is insulated and has tons of overhead storage room PLUS an EV fast charger. A 30x40 metal barn rounds out this property with plenty of space to store extra vehicles, farm equipment, or all of your toys. Expansive land is perfect for horses, cattle, goats, sheep, alpacas, chickens - you name it! Enjoy all that the country has to offer while still being only 11 miles from Falcon shopping and 18 miles from the Powers Corridor.
